{"tid":480172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京幼兒園虐童案 官方聲稱有人造謠被捕","createTime":"2017-11-26T00:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T01:12:34.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67677d8570a9e051dfac760da73e6f18ad30859a","tid":480172,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/800/20171125/30851328.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F800%2F20171125%2F30851328.jpg&h=b5dff0e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京市公安局朝陽分局官方微博「平安朝陽」下午針對此案發出2份情況通報。第一份通一名22歲的劉姓幼兒園女老師因涉嫌虐待被看護人罪，今天已被刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n另一份通報則聲稱，23日逮捕的一名31歲的北京劉姓女子，承認自己編造共軍「老虎團」人員集體猥褻幼兒並透過微信傳播此訊息。目前，劉姓女子因虛構事實擾亂公共秩序，被公安機關行政拘留。<br />\n<br />\n朝陽區政府發言人表示，根據公安機關通報此幼兒園案件的偵辦情況，認為這是一起傷害幼兒的惡劣事件，「社會影響極壞」。"},{"pid":"d9b8716ac6cc64d9f29f744dfe9a49d363052e5d","tid":480172,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b604d2689aea0ec3f2f339f21bab99177529c2c3","tid":480172,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:45:11.000Z","msg":"希望院長其實係無帶啲阿叔阿伯性侵啲3歲小孩搞到佢地肛裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但咁點解要打毒針同餵小朋友餵丸仔"},{"pid":"cb47c4b2d500848f2e29e7fcc3fd6661932e096f","tid":480172,"uid":65587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/e/ea/This_is_part_of_China_Short.gif/revision/latest?cb=20120613165411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fea%2FThis_is_part_of_China_Short.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120613165411&h=128e27ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b2ae753e358a9376290c2056f8d18edc8827248","tid":480172,"uid":10438,"like":0,"dislike":0,